OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,FPeople applying to university will no
OL,7,Flonger have to write an essay for
OL,8,Ftheir personal statement, Ucas has
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FInstead, those applying to start in
OL,12,F2026 will answer three guided
OL,13,Fquestions.
OL,15,FThe admissions body Ucas said it is to
OL,16,Flevel the playing field for
OL,17,Fdisadvantaged students.
