OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,FThe move comes after longstanding
OL,7,Fconcerns that the existing personal
OL,8,Fstatement favours advantaged students
OL,9,Fwho can get more support.
OL,11,FIt is hoped the structured questions
OL,12,Fwill provide students from all
OL,13,Fbackgrounds with a better
OL,14,Funderstanding of the key information
OL,15,Funiversities and colleges want to know
OL,16,Fabout them when making admissions
OL,17,Fdecisions.
