OL,6,FUcas data suggests the gap in
OL,7,Funiversity application rates between
OL,8,Fthe most and least advantaged students
OL,9,Fhas widened in the last year.
OL,11,FCurrently, applicants set out their
OL,12,Fskills, experiences and their reasons
OL,13,Ffor applying for a course in a text
OL,14,Fbox ` which can be up to 4,000
OL,15,Fcharacters.
OL,17,FBut from September 2025, students who
OL,18,Fare applying for 2026 entry to
OL,19,Funiversity or college courses will
OL,20,Fanswer three questions:
