OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,FPrevious Ucas research found 79% of
OL,7,Fstudents felt the process of writing
OL,8,Fthe personal statement was difficult
OL,9,Fto complete without support.
OL,11,FUcas surveyed potential applicants
OL,12,Fabout to start their personal
OL,13,Fstatement, and found more than three-
OL,14,Fquarters prefer the new three-question
OL,15,Fformat.
OL,17,FThe answers to those questions will
OL,18,Fstill be up to 4,000 characters long,
OL,19,Fcombined.
