OL,6,FThe number of 18-year-olds in the UK
OL,7,Fapplying to undergraduate courses has
OL,8,Frisen slightly this year.
OL,10,FBut the application rate from the most
OL,11,Fdisadvantaged backgrounds has fallen
OL,12,Fslightly to 25% in England, while rate
OL,13,Ffor the most advantaged has increased
OL,14,Fto 61%.
OL,16,FJo Saxton, chief executive at Ucas,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Today's figures show that
OL,18,Fwhilst positive progress has been
OL,19,Fmade, there is still much to do.
