OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,F"The changes to the personal
OL,7,Fstatement, along with our recent fee
OL,8,Fwaiver for students in receipt of free
OL,9,Fschool meals, are all part of Ucas's
OL,10,Fcontribution to the sector-wide effort
OL,11,Fto ensure more people from
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged backgrounds can benefit
OL,13,Ffrom the life-changing opportunity of
OL,14,Fhigher education.
OL,16,F"During my time in schools, I saw
OL,17,Ffirst-hand how the personal statement
OL,18,Fcan help students really clarify and
OL,19,Farticulate their ambition, but also
OL,20,Fhow challenging it can be for those
OL,21,Fwith less support.
