OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,F"The new approach, with guided
OL,7,Fquestions, aims to give greater
OL,8,Fconfidence to those students, as well
OL,9,Fas their teachers when advising on how
OL,10,Fto secure their dream course."
OL,12,FKevin Gilmartin, post 16 specialist at
OL,13,Fthe Association of Schools and College
OL,14,FLeaders (ASCL), said: "This is a very
OL,15,Fwelcome change. The current 'text box'
OL,16,Fapproach is far too vague and has
OL,17,Ffavoured students who are able to draw
OL,18,Fon support from family members that
OL,19,Fhave previously been to university and
OL,20,Fsubmitted personal statements
OL,21,Fthemselves.
