OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,F"The switch to structured questions
OL,7,Fwill provide much needed clarity to
OL,8,Fstudents about what information they
OL,9,Fshould be including.
OL,11,F"These questions should also be of
OL,12,Fmore use to admissions tutors than the
OL,13,Fold-style personal statements, which
OL,14,Fresearch has shown were barely being
OL,15,Fread in many cases."
OL,17,FA report by the Higher Education
OL,18,FPolicy Institute (Hepi) think tank
OL,19,Flast year suggested that university
OL,20,Fapplicants' personal statements are
OL,21,Fread for just two minutes on average.
