OL,3,CUniversity applicants no longer need
OL,4,Cto write 4,000-character essay
OL,6,FLee Elliot Major, professor of social
OL,7,Fmobility at the University of Exeter,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This welcome reform strikes the
OL,9,Fright balance between a more
OL,10,Fstructured approach to deter
OL,11,Ffabrication, while not limiting the
OL,12,Fopportunity for applicants to
OL,13,Fpersonalise their statement.
OL,15,F"I believe it is a significant step in
OL,16,Fmaking the university admissions
OL,17,Fsystem a little bit fairer for all
OL,18,Fapplicants."
